      content: '<p>“They know where we are and they just wait for the Libyans to come tomorrow to pick our corpses,” came the anguished call from a boat in distress.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://theintercept.com/2019/06/09/europe-migrants-mediterranean-rescues/">Amid Spike in Migrants Crossing the Mediterranean, Europe Is Still Delaying Rescues</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://theintercept.com">The Intercept</a>.</p>\n',
